Text.Page:
Okay, let's see what we've got for you here.

Looks like {@LinkCreature:9#100#tawny sabertooths}, {@LinkCreature:9#200#mugatos}, and {@LinkCreature:9#310#alpha crocutas} over by the labyrinth.

Clear those out, and report to Noleta when you're through.
We all have a part to play if we're going to defeat the gulas, and keeping those beasts from menacing our soldiers is a "win" in my book.
